	<Folder>
		<name>DRATS 2010</name>
		<open>1</open>
		<description>Gigapans, track logs, plans, image overlays from the Desert Rats trip to part of the San Francisco Volcano field April 5-6, 2010. Lots of work on SP Crater and Colton Crater.</description>
		<LookAt>
			<longitude>-111.6317452179124</longitude>
			<latitude>35.56959029292265</latitude>
			<altitude>0</altitude>
			<range>10018.25882050607</range>
			<tilt>13.23914841259564</tilt>
			<heading>-3.119428867397572</heading>
			<altitudeMode>relativeToGround</altitudeMode>
		</LookAt>
		<Folder>
			<name>Gigapan Plan April 2010</name>
			<open>1</open>
			<description>Initial plan. We had misidentified Colton crater, but once we figured that out , we mostly achieved our objectives.</description>
